{"tid":2431101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"接種中國疫苗現不良反應 男子發燒關節痛出紅疹","createTime":"2021-03-03T11:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T15:05:25.000Z","uid":293677,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"14c9f18d88f50bb172d3e6c17100a0b26e1a750b","tid":2431101,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:43:35.000Z","msg":"2021/03/03 14:31<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">中國北京通州區一名女子在網路上爆料，稱其丈夫接種武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫苗後，身體出現嚴重不良反應，不僅發高燒、關節痛，身上還出現大面積紅疹。她陪同丈夫到多個醫院求診後，醫師不排除與疫苗有關。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中國微博帳號「永遠守護你的福妃」1日貼文表示，她與丈夫2月17日接種疫苗第1劑，2月23日丈夫身上開始出現小紅疹，2月23日開始發高燒38.5度以上，紅疹也開始增多。起初以為是蕁麻疹，但丈夫吃藥後仍高燒不退，2月27日紅疹遍及胸背腰臀、雙臂腿部甚至腳面，渾身疼癢，無法入睡，並出現關節痛。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，27日下午到首都醫科大學附屬北京潞河醫院求診，急診科醫師讓丈夫次日到皮膚科門診，28日丈夫先在醫院的皮膚科做了血液檢查、核酸檢查、CT檢查、生化檢查等，各項結果正常，檢測結果為陰性。雖然醫師沒有給出明確答覆是疫苗後的過敏反應，但是大夫也說「不排除是」。<br />\n<br />\n事後她向政府和潞河醫院反映，但醫院表示「病看好了再說」，她質疑「病好了還怎麼證明是否疫苗的過敏反應」。至3月2日，其丈夫開始退燒好轉。<br />\n<br />\n《明報》 報導，北京目前使用的是<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">國藥集團</span></span>北京研究所和北京<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">科興</span></span>研製的2款武漢肺炎滅活疫苗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3454776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3454776&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=f0dca09c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3454776&h=825296bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3454776</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">咁都打你唔死 算你命硬</span></span>"},{"pid":"3f5a8b6d0b941c4ee7c90207932114fdfb8c9474","tid":2431101,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"慘過死啲CASE點計先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bceb4d39ce541537124e046af9c037605a95fd6","tid":2431101,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:47:27.000Z","msg":"原來係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26663931a86154a77dbe430f3333ae7e0326faba","tid":2431101,"uid":264284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"又想屈政府錢<br />\n又顛覆又叛國<br />\n自首啦"},{"pid":"b45b56852a748c4ecc17ca05423bc778ad80f4d1","tid":2431101,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"醫師不排除與疫苗有關<br />\n又一個李文亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be151486a7d5987e79843eaf2e2bc739303bd678","tid":2431101,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b45b56852a748c4ecc17ca05423bc778ad80f4d1","tid":2431101,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"醫師不排除與疫苗有關<br />\n又一個李文亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"仲有醫德過香港嗰班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca8390b05b2891907153a967f2748bf56d633d7","tid":2431101,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"責任不在中方"},{"pid":"f0813dfe1a9dc286b6e8a082a099f756225cd286","tid":2431101,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"永遠守護你的腹肌"},{"pid":